name: TREATED LIKE VICIOUS ANIMALS
description: USE YOUR VOICE; NOT EVERYONE HAS ONE THAT CAN BE HEARD. BE AN ACTIVE LISTENER. STAND UP FOR OTHERS. SPEAK UP AND SPEAK OUT!
